authnSelectionTrees.name: DSW Store Shared Login - IdP Initiated
authnSelectionTrees.description: DSW Store shared login policy.  Used for IdP initiated application logins that should return the shared user contract for DSW users as well as send shared credentials to the endpoint application.  DSWSHAREDLOGIN=TRUE

authnSelectionTrees.name: DSW Store Shared Login - SP Connection Based
authnSelectionTrees.description: Network and SP Connection targetted Shared Account login applications

authnSelectionTrees.name: OAuth - MFA If External
authnSelectionTrees.description: OAuth policy to require PingID MFA if the login is coming from external/off corporate network

authnSelectionTrees.name: OAuth - MFA None
authnSelectionTrees.description: Never MFA for OAuth clients bound to this policy

authnSelectionTrees.name: No MFA
authnSelectionTrees.description: Policy that never requires MFA authentication.

authnSelectionTrees.name: Only If External MFA
authnSelectionTrees.description: Policy that prompts for MFA only when the user is external.

authnSelectionTrees.name: Always MFA
authnSelectionTrees.description: Policy that requires MFA regardless of the users location/dispostion.

authnSelectionTrees.name: HTML Form Only MFA
authnSelectionTrees.description: Forms based authentication only policy.  External MFA only.  Targetted use for systems with Privlidged Access accounts logging in that need to bypass MFA for those targeted accounts.
